plans/*.yaml
terraform/.terraform/
terraform/.terraform.lock.hcl
terraform/terraform.tfstate*
terraform/*.tfvars

# The repo-root `**/target` rule (Rust build dirs) also matches this demo's
# target *app* directory and hides its source. Re-include the dir (required —
# the parent dir is what's excluded) so the Go source terraform reads at apply
# time (compute.tf: file("../target/main.go")) is actually committed.
!target/
!target/main.go
